{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-situations-page-tsx","path":"/en/situations/shops-and-services/repair-shops-and-after-sale-services","result":{"data":{"situation":{"title":"Repair shops and after-sale services","meta_description":"Retail sale and the provision of service are not allowed, there are, however, certain exceptions.","content":{"processed":"<h2>Pravidla a doporučení</h2>\n<p>Obecně jsou maloobchodní prodej a poskytování služeb zakázány. Z tohoto zákazu ale existují <strong>výjimky, mezi kterými jsou uvedeny i některé opravny a servisy. </strong></p>\n<p>Konkrétně mohou být otevřeny <strong>autoservisy</strong> a <strong>cykloservisy</strong>. Dále mohou fungovat i <strong>servisy</strong> <strong>a opravny elektroniky</strong> a <strong>přístrojů</strong> <strong>pro</strong> <strong>domácnost</strong>. Otevřené jsou i <strong>myčky</strong> <strong>automobilů</strong>.</p>\n<p><strong>Ostatní opravny a servisy, které nejsou ve výjimkách, musí být uzavřeny.</strong></p>\n"},"path":{"alias":"/situations/shops-and-services/repair-shops-and-after-sale-services"},"changed":"2020-11-19T09:52:48+00:00","valid_from":"2020-11-04T00:00:00+01:00","langcode":"en","created":"2020-11-05T21:38:55+00:00","links":[{"uri":"https://www.vlada.cz/assets/media-centrum/aktualne/uv201116-1192.pdf","title":"The ban on the provision of services is regulated by governmental measures "}],"relationships":{"region":[{"name":"All regions of Czechia"}],"icon":{"code":"electrical_services"},"situation_type":{"name":"Shops and services","path":{"alias":"/situations/shops-and-services"},"relationships":{"icon":{"code":"storefront"}}},"measures":[],"related_situations":[{"title":"Retail","path":{"alias":"/situations/shops-and-services/retail","langcode":"en"}},{"title":"Shopping","path":{"alias":"/situations/shops-and-services/shopping","langcode":"en"}},{"title":"Services","path":{"alias":"/situations/shops-and-services/services","langcode":"en"}},{"title":"Buying real es